Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:11.30,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.41,0:00:15.73,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.73,0:00:23.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.23,0:00:27.08,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:30.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.81,0:00:34.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:37.93,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:45.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Tearing through the\Nair with a Rider Plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:53.12,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great flight that\Nskates over the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.12,0:00:56.88,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up tornadoes with a Rider Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.88,0:01:00.78,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.78,0:01:04.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.52,0:01:08.34,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:11.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:15.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:19.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:25.02,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx120\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,160.389)}The True Identity of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:25.02,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,720.389)}Gel Shocker's Leader!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.45,0:01:30.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A deadly battle between Kamen Riders\Nand Shocker Riders has broken out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.74,0:01:33.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,over the secret behind\NGel Shocker's leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:38.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Six Shocker Riders surrounded\Nthe first and second Kamen Riders.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.19,0:01:41.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And the computer tape filled\Nwith secret information
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:44.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,was on the verge of being stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Ichimonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... we'll hit them all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.49,0:02:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! The Riders have lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Still alive, are they? Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay quiet, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tachibana!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.73,0:03:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kogure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The Anti-Shocker Alliance is with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Riders are struggling...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll support them with a gas shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did the Riders go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.35,0:04:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Double Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.05,0:04:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! The Riders are after the helicopter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... we got a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We almost had them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Riders have escaped,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you lost your hostages,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and the computer tape is back\Nwith the Anti-Shocker Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you intend to do about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Worry not, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:04:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I have another plan in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sure of it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the correct computer tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.43,0:05:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, when will you have it ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.73,0:05:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The computer that Gel Shocker damaged\Nwill be repaired tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.76,0:05:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow morning, eh? I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. Why don't you come to watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd love to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... as long as they don't make\Nanother try for it, at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If I seal it in here,\Nnot even Gel Shocker will find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Raydokuga?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't moved since we brought him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He has the power to put others to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.18,0:06:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he can self-hypnotize, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all riding on tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, keep a close watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.48,0:06:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I happen to have both\NHongo and Hayato both here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll have a long overdue training session.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Those six Shocker Riders\Nare powerful, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it. I'll handle things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,These training grounds
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,are where you've put your lives\Non the line to acquire new abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, we're facing\Nthe six Shocker Riders,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,who have the same abilities we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to defeat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops. Please, train us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The individual abilities of the\NShocker Riders are equal to yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And they also have special\Nabilities unique to monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't be easy to beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But to fight against Gel Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is the path we've been given.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll have some\Nspecial training today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to run in a circle around me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Speed up more!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,More speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Rider Wheel Training!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Speed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You need more speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:07:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Run again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:08:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Go faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster! More speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Haven't you gotten a\Ntransmission from Raydokuga yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing on the radar screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He should start putting out\Nradio waves any time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,When he wakes up, we get to extract\Nthe location of Gel Shocker's base from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.91,0:08:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still asleep, as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I just saw him move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still fast asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I imagined it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.05,0:09:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black, the radar's picking up\NRaydokuga's transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.76,0:09:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Slug Mushroom! Prepare to deploy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.98,0:09:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll destroy the Kamen Rider at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:38.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,You were killed by Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:42.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now, at last, my long\Njourney will come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:45.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Once we know their leader's identity...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:57.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,That's right. Your long\Njourney is at an end!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:09:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the computer tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I might even spare your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't! You'll have to kill me first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.25,0:10:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I have other ways to take it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.30,0:10:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to die... I'll oblige you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kogure! What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kogure! Speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:11:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A new monster...\Nattacked me out of nowhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the tape still in the safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, Gel Shocker has a\Nnew monster already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? An earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:31.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Anti-Shocker Alliance...\Nyour guards cannot stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice sounds like Raydokuga!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.78,0:11:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.37,0:11:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.94,0:11:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.93,0:11:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Raydokuga!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.30,0:11:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,None can oppose Gel Shocker and live!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker... transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:37.97,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.73,0:12:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Raydokuga got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Mr. Kogure? Is the tape safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. They're both just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.61,0:12:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as the tape's safe,\Nwe've still got the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.89,0:13:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Raydokuga got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If Raydokuga is out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't afford to sit around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll probably be back with\Nthose awful Shocker Riders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Let's move to the computer room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we'll finally know the\Nidentity of Gel Shocker's leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm turning it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"Gel Shocker's leader is in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Location: 70 degrees to the northeast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Distance: 120 kilometers."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Near Mount Tsukuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where their leader is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.13,0:14:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Let's get going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll finally avenge everyone we lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Raydokuga!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You followed us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you reach our leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:14:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.63,0:15:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Drill Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You think they'll be enough to stop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.21,0:16:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's always a Kamen Rider on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Riders!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost to our destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You think we'll find their\Nleader in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be a base hidden\Nsomewhere around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the entrance to your base?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:17:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.88,0:18:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right.\N- Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's their leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's find out who it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.27,0:18:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.04,0:18:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You've finally arrived,\Nfirst and second Kamen Riders.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally arrived?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean this was all a trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.51,0:18:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A trap to wipe Kamen Rider\Nfrom the face of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.22,0:18:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I leaked false data to the Anti-Shocker\NAlliance's computer that I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:19:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The end of Kamen Rider is near.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, die at the hands\Nof the Shocker Riders!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.07,0:19:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kogure is missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So is Chie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kogure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.69,0:19:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you gone mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.49,0:19:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kogure is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.61,0:19:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you who I really am...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Slug Mushroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.18,0:19:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Slug Mushroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl is all that remains\Nof the Anti-Shocker Alliance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right!\N- Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:51.64,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:55.06,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:19:59.08,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:02.64,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:06.21,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:09.83,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.01,0:20:12.38,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.19,0:20:15.63,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:20.55,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:23.83,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.28,0:20:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,with its armies made of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:53.23,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my scarf of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:56.13,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.67,0:20:59.17,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.17,0:21:03.65,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:06.90,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:17.95,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:21.31,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies spreading fear
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.79,0:21:25.45,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten our towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:28.73,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.97,0:21:32.46,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.46,0:21:35.87,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my mask of green...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.20,0:21:39.30,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.85,0:21:42.65,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:46.96,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.96,0:21:50.21,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:21:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Riders... you can't escape now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.45,0:21:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even he can stand\Nagainst six Shocker Riders!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.68,0:21:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll all follow soon after!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.27,0:21:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! The Rider Wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.69,0:21:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Ichimonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.69,0:21:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.73,0:22:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.76,0:22:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You survived?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.54,0:22:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The fakes are all dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,An imposter can't beat the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.13,0:22:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.81,0:22:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.22,0:22:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Double Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.17,0:23:04.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The two Kamen Riders had escaped the\Nterrible trap set by Gel Shocker's leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.72,0:23:07.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But when would they\Nfinally learn his identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:11.14,Cont,,0,90,160,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.24,0:23:14.18,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(300.175,262.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.77,0:23:16.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The monstrous Garaox\Nbreathes out a deadly gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.72,0:23:21.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The gas causes anything it touches to\Nrise into the air like a hot air balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.13,0:23:24.53,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A breathtaking fight unfurls between\NGaraox and the Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.53,0:23:27.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in a vehicle 500 meters in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:31.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for more Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.74,0:23:31.24,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,190.389)}The Monstrous Garaox's
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.74,0:23:31.24,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx140\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,710.389)}Flying Cars!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.05,0:23:39.40,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,The wind gusts across the wasteland
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.40,0:23:42.74,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider traverses it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.74,0:23:46.77,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Alone, all alone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.77,0:23:50.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Holding back my sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.02,0:23:53.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,I fight, I fight alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.94,0:24:01.24,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Despite my solitude,\NI will do what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.24,0:24:06.37,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,to protect my friends and my home
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.37,0:24:12.55,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,I am the Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The True Identity of\NGel Shocker's Leader!!
Comment: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Monstrous Garaox's\NFlying Cars!!\NJoin us next week for more Kamen Rider!